sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Server

    (user adds new note)
    Browser->>Server: POST /new_note (note data)
    Server->>Server: save note to db
    Server->>Browser: redirect to /notes after updating
    Browser->>Server: GET /notes (reloads, fetches new js code)
    Server->>Browser: HTML page with updated notes
    Browser->>User: render updated page
